{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "第十五回 苦差\n\n梅汝男主动约郭大路到院中谈话，郭大路误以为梅汝男看上了自己，结果梅汝男坦白真正喜欢的人是燕七。梅汝男解释她是故意与郭大路亲近来刺激燕七，因为她喜欢不拘小节、有男子气概的男人。郭大路回到屋中将此事告知燕七，燕七兴奋地跑出去见梅汝男，却被梅汝男抓伤了脸。梅汝男最终改变了嫁给燕七的主意，燕七只说了一句话就让她改变了心意，但燕七拒绝透露这句话的内容。王动借此讨论了朋友之间也应有秘密的道理，强调每个人都有权保留自己的秘密。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我祖宗一定积了德，否则怎会交到你们这种好朋友呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你在说什么？为什么还不出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "我什么也没有说，我在放屁。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到这人原来也会装蒜的，心里明明喜欢得要命，却偏偏要装出这种愁眉苦脸的样子，叫人看着生气。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "你弄错了一件事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "他心里并不喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "不喜欢，梅姑娘难道还配不上他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "配不配得上是一回事，喜不喜欢又是另外一回事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你怎么知道他不喜欢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "因为他还没有变成呆子，也没有变成哑巴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "text": "有个很聪明的人说过一句很有道理的话，他说，无论多聪明的人，若是真的喜欢上一个女人，他在她面前也一定会变得呆头呆脑的，甚至连话都说不出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "但他在梅姑娘面前，说的话还是比别人多……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这只因有的人天生就是多嘴婆。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "有什么麻烦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "我本来还想一见面就先想法子把他灌醉的，免得他想起昨天的事，故意找我的麻烦。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你若怕他找你麻烦，不妨躲着他些，等过几天他的气平了后，再去见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "你不是急着要我回去见他吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你以为……你以为……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "不是我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "不是我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "是燕七。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "燕七？……你看上的人是燕七？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "我实在不懂，你怎么会看上他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我觉得他很好，样样都好。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "连不洗澡那样也好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "有个性的男人，在没有成亲的时候，常常都不修边幅的，但等到有了个妻子照顾他的时间，他就会变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "老实说，我从小就喜欢这种不拘小节的男人，这种人才真的有男子气。那种成天打扮得油头粉脸的男人，我一看就要吐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我也知道他总是在躲着我，好像很讨厌我，其实真正有性格的男人都是这样子的。那种一见了女人就像苍蝇见了血的男人，我更讨厌。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "这么样说来，你是真的很喜欢他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你连一点也看不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "我只觉得你好像跟我特别亲热。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那不过是我故意逗他生气了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "你既然喜欢他，为什么反而要逗他生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "就因为我喜欢他，所以才要逗他生气，这道理你也不懂？",
      "tone": "调皮",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "这么样看来，一个男人还是莫要被女人看上的好，若是永远都没有女人看上他，他活得反而开心些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你现在很开心么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "text": "当然很开心，简直开心极了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你今天怎么回事？变成了酒坛子吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "好朋友的喜酒当然要多喝几杯，你难道舍不得？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这里倒的确有个新郎倌，但却不是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不是你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你看什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "看你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我有什么好看的？你只怕看错了人吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我正是想找出你这人究竟有什么好看的地方，会有人看上你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "谁看上了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "新娘子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "新娘子跟我又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "新娘子若是跟新郎倌没有关系，跟谁有关系？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "谁是新郎倌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "原来你也很喜欢她。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你若是不喜欢她，为什么笑得这么开心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她的人呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "正在院子里等新郎倌，你最好不要让她等太着急。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来新郎倌比新娘子还急。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你是不是很不服气？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我只不过觉得有点奇怪。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "有什么好奇怪的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我只奇怪，为什么每个女人的眼睛都有毛病。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你认为这姑娘怎会看上燕七的？你认为他很丑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "其实他也不能叫做太丑，至少他的眼睛并不丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他鼻子很丑吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "也不算是很丑，只不过笑起来的时候就像个肉包子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他的嘴很丑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我很少看到他的嘴。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他的嘴好像比金毛狮子狗的嘴还要小。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "小嘴很难看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他什么地方难看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "他若是常洗洗澡，也许并不是个很难看的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "若真的他洗个澡，你也许会吓一跳。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我倒真希望他什么时候能让我吓一跳。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你既然也觉得他不错，那么梅姑娘看上他，又有什么不对呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "对，对极了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道新郎倌都很急，却还是没想到燕七会急得这么厉害。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "新娘子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "没有新娘子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "有新郎倌，就有新娘子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "也没有新郎倌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "新娘子是不是已经被新郎倌吓跑了？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她的确已经走了，但却不是被我吓走的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不是？你没有动手动脚，她为什么会叫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我若真的动手动脚，她还会走吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为，她忽然改变了主意，不想嫁给我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "她改变了主意？怎么会的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为……因为我对她说了一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我不信，一个女人若已打定了主意要嫁给你，你就算说三千六百句话，她也不会改变主意。",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你几时看过有人肯让已钓上手的鱼溜走的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "也许她忽然发现这条鱼刺太多，也许她根本不喜欢吃鱼。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "天下没有不喜欢吃鱼的猫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她不是猫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "若不是猫，怎么会抓人呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你究竟是用什么法子，让她改变主意的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我什么法子也没有用，只不过说了一句话而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "说的什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那是我的事，你为什么一定要问？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "因为我也想学学。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为什么要学？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "只要是男人，谁不想学？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那我更不能告诉你了。",
      "tone": "调皮",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为那是我的秘密，若被你学会，我还有什么戏唱？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我还以为你是我朋友哩，谁知你连……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "朋友之间难道就不能有秘密？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "那也要看是什么样的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "秘密就是秘密，所有的秘密都一样。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这么样说来，你也有秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你呢？你难道没有？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "别人若要问你的秘密，你肯不肯说？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那么你就也不能问别人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    }
